  theme: {
    extend: {
      fontFamily: {
        geist: ["GeistVF", "sans-serif"],
        geistMono: ["GeistMonoVF", "monospace"],
      },
    },
  },
};
Link Fonts in CSS: In your globals.css file, use @font-face to define these fonts:

css
Copy
Edit
